More than 2,000 people from around the world have applied for <PEPERO AGENT:P>

We thank you for all your love and support❤️

Now, it’s time to announce the 111 Agents who will take on a series of 4 PEPERO Missions for a chance to become one of the 11 Finalists!

Don’t forget to like and share to show your support for the 111 Agents🤎

※All selected 111 agents will be contacted individually via DM from @pepero.agentp and will receive an official confirmation email from pepero.agentp@gmail.com.
※This announcement is based on Instagram usernames. 
※ Individual DM notifications to 111 Agents will be sent out gradually starting from July 1 (KST)

As my @Pepero.Official mission 1️⃣ is now completed, I want to bring you behind the scene to find out where to locate your favourite Pepero 🎯

I got the original for the kids (July 20 is @Frenchie.Latte‘s 5th birthday 🎂) but Agent Bok ➕ Agent Pup wanted to try more flavours.

Made a stop @FoodyWorldGTA and found crunchy, white+cookie, choco cookie, choco filled, almond and snowy almond.

As Agent Bok loves strawberry 🍓 I got to drop by @HMartToronto to grab him a box.

First mission is officially over and thank you for your support. Please like, comment and share the 💙 for Pepero!
